org.apache.gora.persistency.impl

Class DirtyCollectionWrapper<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.gora.persistency.impl.DirtyCollectionWrapper<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the list that this wrapper wraps.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<T>, Collection<T>, Dirtyable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DirtyListWrapper, DirtySetWrapper

    public class DirtyCollectionWrapper<T>
extends Object
implements Dirtyable, Collection<T>
    A List implementation that wraps another list, intercepting modifications to the list structure and reporting on weather or not the list has been modified, and also checking list elements for modification.
